import * as d3 from 'd3';

export function drawChart(height, width){
    d3.select("#chart")
        .append("svg")
        .attr("width", width)
        .attr("height", height)
        .style("border", "1px solid black")
        .append("text")
        .attr("fill", "green")
        .attr("x", 50)
        .attr("y", 50)
        .text("Hello D3")
}
